message.content: cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM. The paper deals with video understanding and question answering, which are topics related to computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also proposes a model that combines visual and textual content, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper introduces a new dataset for video question answering, which is relevant to multimedia (cs.MM).
